T1  - Estimation of the Pareto law from underreported data: A further analysis
AU  - Hinkley, David V.
AU  - Revankar, Nagesh S.
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 5
IS  - 1
SP  - 1
EP  - 11
PY  - 1977
DA  - 1977/01/01/
